<plot>The Pascadelli's are in trouble. This once proud organized crime family is no longer organized. In fact, they are completely inept and falling apart at the seams. Just ask filmmaker Robert Brewer. He's the acclaimed director that was hired to document the family's recent fall from grace. What the classic mockumentary "This Is Spinal Tap" did for rock stars, "Hit" equally does for the mob as it chronicles the dysfunctional Pascadelli underworld in all its hilarious glory.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?241617</url></doc>
